          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong>,<strong> soft cheese</strong> and <strong>chopped tomatoes </strong>to the pan with the sausage and give everything a good stir</p><p>Cook for 3 min further or until the sauce thickens slightly and the sausage is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-copy-3-1644923893055-x200.jpg",
