    {
      "instruction": "<p>Stir the <strong>drained tortelloni </strong>and <strong>half </strong>of your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) into the sauce<strong> </strong>and give everything a gentle mix up until the pasta is coated in the sauce</p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p>",
